OL,5, More than half of Scotland's           
OL,6, hospitality businesses could close     
OL,7, without immediate action on soaring    
OL,8, energy costs, the new prime minister   
OL,9, has been warned.                       
OL,11,FWith bills rising by up to 400%, bosses
OL,12,Fsay the industry will be decimated     
OL,13,Fwithout a pandemic-style response.     
OL,15,FLiz Truss made tackling the            
OL,16,Fcost-of-living crisis one of her top   
OL,17,Fpriorities after entering Number 10.   
OL,19,FShe is set to announce a new package of
OL,20,Fmeasures on Thursday.                  
